skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tea cup
des: Tea Cup allows you to ask about certain types of tea and it will provide a description. It will also allow you to ask about certain symptoms and it will suggest a natural remedy ingredient to use in your tea. Tea Cup is being updated weekly with the latest information purely by experience. Tea Cup does not substitute for professional advice. If you have recurring health issues you may want to consult a physician.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
